updatePrivilegedRole("DB_Admin", ["Read", "Write"]);
System.out.println("DB_Admin role permissions updated to Read, Write");
Output Example:-
DB_Admin role permissions updated to Read, Write.
----------------------------------------------------
()deletePrivilegedRole(roleName):-
Purpose: Role delete karna.
deletePrivilegedRole("DB_Admin");
System.out.println("DB_Admin role deleted");
Output Example:-
DB_Admin role deleted
--------------------------------------------------
()assignRoleToUser(user, role):-
Purpose: Role assign karna.
assignRoleToUser("dev01", "DB_Admin");
System.out.println("DB_Admin role assigned to dev01");
Output Example:-
DB_Admin role assigned to dev01
----------------------------------------------------
()revokeRoleFromUser(user, role):-
Purpose: Role revoke karna.
revokeRoleFromUser("dev01", "DB_Admin");
System.out.println("DB_Admin role revoked from dev01");
Output Example:-
DB_Admin role revoked from dev01
